{"build_type":"library","description":"Cooperative scheduler loop, our own wait/wake with NO futex and NO eventfd. State buffer s: slot 0 ready-stack top count, slots above task ids; slot 10 channel has_data, 11 value, 12 waiter task id (-1 none); slot 20 consumer pc, 22 result, 23 woke. Pops a ready task and runs its step. A consumer with no channel data PARKS (registers as waiter, sets resume pc, yields WITHOUT requeuing -- no futex). A producer deposits the value, marks has_data, and on COMPLETION re-readies any waiter by pushing it onto the ready stack (the completion itself is the wake, all in scheduler state, no eventfd). Tail-recurses until the ready stack is empty. Body built via edit.","module_name":"drive-cooperative-scheduler-until-quiescent","package_name":"drive-cooperative-scheduler-until-quiescent","function_definitions":{"drive-cooperative-scheduler-until-quiescent":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"s","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"negone","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":-1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"beef","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":48879},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c10","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":10},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c11","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":11},{